com.hcl.domino.data

Enum DocumentClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DocumentClass>
      • com.hcl.domino.data.DocumentClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INumberEnum<Short>, Serializable, Comparable<DocumentClass>

    public enum DocumentClass
extends Enum<DocumentClass>
implements INumberEnum<Short>
    These bit masks define the types of notes in a database. The bit masks may be or'ed together to specify more than one type of note.
